  "body": "The goal here is to expose some settings in status-go so it's possible to configure the desktop node as a full node.\r\n\r\nThis builds on top of #2877 , so instead of a toggle we want now a slider or drop down menu with 3 options ( we can think about the exact wording for this later)\r\n\r\n- light node - bloom filter disabled\r\n- normal node - bloom filter enabled\r\n- full node - uses an empty bloom filter so all messages are forwarded\r\n",
